'''余劍明'''（{{lang-en|Lucina Yu Kim Ming}}，{{bd|1969年|4月10日}}），香港著名女唱片騎師及歌手。1985年於[[英華女學校|英華女學校]]中五畢業後暑假參加[[香港電台|香港電台]]主辦「業餘DJ大賽」奪得冠軍隨即加入DJ訓練班<ref>[https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E4%BD%99%E5%8A%8D%E6%98%8E&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E4%BD%99%E5%8A%8D%E6%98%8E%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E4%BD%99%E5%8A%8D%E6%98%8E%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E4%BD%99%E5%8A%8D%E6%98%8E%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E4%BD%99%E5%8A%8D%E6%98%8E%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E4%BD%99%E5%8A%8D%E6%98%8E%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E4%BD%99%E5%8A%8D%E6%98%8E%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58Sngm8Qm6Mn%2FFheWB6hLBZ&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=2&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc 明日DJ邁向第一步 余劍明過關斬將] {{Wayback|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E4%BD%99%E5%8A%8D%E6%98%8E&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E4%BD%99%E5%8A%8D%E6%98%8E%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E4%BD%99%E5%8A%8D%E6%98%8E%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E4%BD%99%E5%8A%8D%E6%98%8E%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E4%BD%99%E5%8A%8D%E6%98%8E%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E4%BD%99%E5%8A%8D%E6%98%8E%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E4%BD%99%E5%8A%8D%E6%98%8E%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58Sngm8Qm6Mn%2FFheWB6hLBZ&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=2&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc |date=20201119204713 }} [[華僑日報|華僑日報]]. 1985-09-02</ref>，並原校升讀預科，同年還參加了[[西區社區中心|西區社區中心]]青毅服務團主辦「仲夏夜弦歌比賽」以一曲《[[長夜_My_Love_Goodnight|長夜 My Love Goodnight]]》奪得獨唱組冠軍<ref>[https:/